data.description: Don't miss this upgraded Victoria and enjoy this Golf Bundled Home with exceptional resort amenities.   Nestled with a reserve behind it and loads of nature all around.  This home will catch your eye immediately.  Professionally decorated with upgraded lighting, floors, paint and fixtures.  This home features exceptional outdoor living with a newly installed outdoor kitchen, in ground pool and spa and a half bath just off the pool.  Inside enjoy your split bedrooms and an office to work from home, do hobbies or turn into that third bedroom.  Too many upgrades to list.  Amazing feature wall in the dining room with a fireplace.
